data.description: No Flood Insurance Required! Welcome to your waterfront paradise! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, nestled on 1/4 acre of prime real estate, offers the best of both worlds – a luxurious retreat for all, and a lake boater's dream come true.  Step inside and be amazed by the spacious open floor plan, complete with vaulted ceilings, an elegant kitchen – just waiting for you to choose your favorite countertops and a versatile den. The expansive glass doors in the living area provide breathtaking views of Lake Kennedy, immersing you in the natural beauty of this serene location.  Outside, the custom heated pool invites you to take a dip, while the generous patio area is perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying the sunset with your loved ones. Those who love to fish, the freshwater lake in your backyard offers endless opportunities to reel in a catch, or simply unwind on your boat or jetski as you take in the idyllic surroundings.  This exceptional property boasts a new roof, a 2-car garage, and the peace of mind that comes with being located in a No Flood Zone. Don't let this opportunity pass you by – make this waterfront haven your new home and start creating cherished memories today!
